  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Social support for the poor in communities though innovative approaches</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will enable partners among Russian CSOs to improve their social support to the poor people in communities, especially in access to healthcare and other social services. It will encourage CSOs to introduce innovative models such as text messages for awareness raising, volunterism, creative fundraising and social marketing; governance structures at the community/regional levels such as public councils at hospitals, rights ombudsman&apos;s offices. The project will promote best practice and innovations in social contracting for government services by Russian CSOs.</narrative>
  </description>
